ASoC: rockchip: pdm: Add support for path map

This patch adds property 'rockchip,path-map' for path mapping.

e.g.

"rockchip,path-map = <3 2 1 0>" means the mapping as follows:

  path0 <-- sdi3
  path1 <-- sdi2
  path2 <-- sdi1
  path3 <-- sdi0

